OL,3,CWorld class hat maker inspired by
OL,4,CWelsh hometown
OL,6,FAlison Tod is one of the world's
OL,7,Fleading milliners. Her work has been
OL,8,Fpublished in top flight fashion
OL,9,Fmagazines, with some of the biggest
OL,10,Fnames in fashion including Dior,
OL,11,FChanel and Louis Vuitton.
OL,13,FThis summer she was one of fifteen hat
OL,14,Fmakers from across the world to be an
OL,15,Fofficial milliner for Royal Ascot,
OL,16,Fdescribing it as "the biggest thing
OL,17,Fwe've been recognised as".
