OL,4,CWelsh hometown
OL,6,FIn 1990, Tod set up her business in
OL,7,FAbergavenny because she wanted to
OL,8,Freturn home: "I just love it here, and
OL,9,FI was quite homesick in London - I was
OL,10,Fjust on that train every weekend as
OL,11,Fsoon as I could to come home!"
OL,13,F"I think we're a very talented,
OL,14,Fclever, caring nation and I think you
OL,15,Ffeel that when you're in any Welsh
OL,16,Fcommunity... so to have a business
OL,17,Fhere was really a very easy call"
