OL,3,CWorld class hat maker inspired by
OL,4,CWelsh hometown
OL,6,FShe says the colours of Abergavenny
OL,7,Finspire her - whether that's the flame
OL,8,For turquoise skies, or the huge
OL,9,Fhydrangeas that used to grow close to
OL,10,Fher childhood home in an old boathouse.
OL,12,FShe's won the Welsh Fashion Awards,
OL,13,Ftwo years running, adding "I think our
OL,14,Ffashion is really up there with Paris,
OL,15,FMadrid and Barcelona - I think we do
OL,16,Fhave a very strong Celtic flare" -
OL,17,Fwith customers that come from right
OL,18,Facross Wales and further afield.
