OL,6,FAt her boutique in Abergavenny, she
OL,7,Fwants customers to feel like they've
OL,8,Fentered a 'fairytale', to be taken
OL,9,Faway from reality and delight in the
OL,10,Fcreations. She has a workshop above
OL,11,Fthe shop, with her work having a
OL,12,Fsculptural feel about it. Much of it
OL,13,Fis designed as she works with the
OL,14,Fmaterials: "For me you draw with your
OL,15,Fhands and your eyes".
OL,17,FShe says she enjoys working with the
OL,18,Fteam around her, who have a background
OL,19,Fin various disciplines including fine
OL,20,Fart and fashion.
