OL,6,FSusan Allen has been a customer since
OL,7,Fshe first spotted the shop on a trip
OL,8,Fto Abergavenny. A regular at Royal
OL,9,FAscot Ladies' Day, she meticulously
OL,10,Fplans her outfit for the day, with the
OL,11,Fhats centre stage. Tod and her team
OL,12,Fhave created many pieces for her, with
OL,13,FSusan saying this year's piece
OL,14,Finvolving hand sewn details and
OL,15,Fspecially dyed feather, left her
OL,16,F"feeling like a film star all day"
