OL,6,F"I came in as a customer and I left as
OL,7,Fa friend.... It doesn't matter if
OL,8,Fyou're a cleaner or a Queen, you'll
OL,9,Fhave the VIP treatment from Alison" -
OL,10,FSusan Allen, customer and friend.
OL,12,FFollowing the Royal Ascot accolade,
OL,13,FTod's next ambition would be to do a
OL,14,Fcollection with a top fashion house,
OL,15,Fas well as dressing the Princess of
OL,16,FWales.
